{"raw_text": "Chapter 3\n\nThe analysis presented in this chapter is based on the WHO Mortality Database as of January 2026, which includes deaths registered in national vital registration systems, with underlying cause of death as coded by the relevant national authority. These data are official national statistics in the sense that they have been transmitted to WHO by the\n\nReferences1\n\n1. Child mortality, stillbirth, and causes of death estimates [online database]. New York, NY: UN Inter-agency Group for Child Mortality Estimation; 2025 (https://childmortality.org/).\n\n2. WHO methods and data sources for life tables 2000\u20132021. Geneva: World Health Organization; 2024 (https://cdn.who.int/media/ docs/default-source/gho-documents/global- health-estimates/ghe2021_lifetable_methods. pdf?sfvrsn=a21ddfdb_1).\n\n3. Methods for estimating the excess mortality associated with the COVID-19 pandemic. Geneva: World Health Organization; 2023 (https://www. who.int/publications/m/item/methods-for-\n\n1 The references were all accessed on 23 March 2026, unless otherwise noted.\n\nAnnex: Summary of the methods\n\ncompetent authorities of the countries concerned (6). The completeness figures draw on analysis of the global health estimates 2023 which is explained in Chapter 2. The country stories were prepared in collaboration with WHO regional offices, WHO country offices and government officials.\n\nestimating-the-excess-mortality-associatedwith- the-covid-19-pandemic).\n\n4. Technical Advisory Group on COVID-19 Mortality Assessment. [internet]. Geneva: World Health Organization; 2026 (https://www.who.int/data/ technical-advisory-group/covid-19--mortality- assessment/membership).\n\n5. Global health estimates 2023. [internet]. Geneva: World Health Organization; 2026 (forthcoming).\n\n6. WHO Mortality Database [online database]. Geneva: World Health Organization; 2026 (https:// www.who.int/data/data-collection-tools/who- mortality-database, accessed 31 January 2026).\n\n59\n\nWorld Health Organization Avenue Appia 20, CH 1211 Geneva 27 Switzerland", "tables_html": [], "images_base64": ["